                                        <span>Published: </span>November 30, 2012 </h6>
                                    <h6 class="kicker">Neediest Cases | One Year Later</h6>
                                    <h1>Young Men Finding Their Way</h1>
                                </div>
                                <div class="storySummary">
                                    <span class="summary">Over the course of the 2012-13 Neediest Cases campaign, The New York Times is catching up on some of the people who were profiled as part of recent campaigns. In the first of two parts, we revisit young men who despite past hardships are moving forward with their careers.</span>
